The Football League Show 18.01.2014

Duration: 1 hour 18 min

Derby's fortunes have been transformed since the arrival of manager Steve McLaren, and the Rams meet another side with promotion ambitions, Brighton.

There are extended highlights of Saturday's early kick-off as Leeds go head to head with Leicester and there is the best of the action from Nottingham Forest's clash with Blackburn Rovers.
